title: Mike Olender from Endeavor/Burnt By The Sun/River Black
itunes:title: Mike Olender from Endeavor/Burnt By The Sun/River Black
description:
Episode 269 - One of my all time favorite vocalists is hanging out on the show this week, Mike Olender from Endeavor/Burnt by the Sun and most recently River Black, hangs out as he waits for a ride to the airport. We get into politics, art as commerce and weird vocals. We definitely go to places I haven’t on this show before, so listen up! Simple Mobile is your perfect sidekick for all your summer adventures!Use our Amazon Affiliate Code to support the show!
